Package ca.corefacility.gview.style.datastyle.mapper

Defines classes which can be used to map certain properties of features to style properties used to display those features.

See: Description

    Interface Description
    ContinuousPropertyMapper  
    ContinuousStyleMapper  
    DiscretePropertyMapper  
    DiscreteStyleMapper  
    PropertyMappable
    This allows (data) styles with property mappers to interface.
    PropertyStyleMapper
    Classes which implement PropertyStyle will be able to perform a mapping between a Feature property and a FeatureItem style aspect.
